OL,3,CMan arrested after five people injured
OL,4,Cas car crashes into pub
OL,6,FA man has been arrested and five
OL,7,Fpeople have been injured after a car
OL,8,Fcrashed into a pub in Bristol.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,11,FMerchants Arms, on Merchants Road in
OL,12,Fthe Hotwells area of the city, at
OL,13,Faround 9.30pm on Sunday 28 March.
OL,15,FAvon and Somerset Police said five
OL,16,Fpeople were injured in the collision.
OL,17,FFour of the injured people were taken
OL,18,Fto hospital, but their injuries were
OL,19,Fnot believed to be serious.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
