CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1774980701
OL,3,CMan arrested after five people injured
OL,4,Cas car crashes into pub
OL,6,FThe force said officers arrested a man
OL,7,Fon suspicion of dangerous driving and
OL,8,Fdriving while unfit through drugs. He
OL,9,Fremains in police custody.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for Avon and Somerset
OL,12,FPolice said: "At 9.28pm on Sunday 29
OL,13,FMarch, we received reports that a car
OL,14,Fhad collided with a building in
OL,15,FMerchants Road in the Hotwells area of
OL,16,FBristol.
OL,18,F"Officers attended, alongside the
OL,19,Fambulance and fire services, and
OL,20,Fclosed the road while they responded.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
