PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1774980701
OL,3,CMan arrested after five people injured
OL,4,Cas car crashes into pub
OL,6,F"Five people were injured and four of
OL,7,Fthese were taken to hospital. None of
OL,8,Fthe injuries were believed to be
OL,9,Fserious.
OL,11,F"A man was arrested at the scene on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of driving a motor vehicle
OL,13,Fdangerously and driving whilst unfit
OL,14,Fthrough drugs. He remains in police
OL,15,Fcustody.
OL,17,FThe force has appealed for anyone with
OL,18,Fdashcam or CCTV footage of the
OL,19,Fcollision to come forward.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
